  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516280/extras/c298b25b34ca624151039072ab892d12.avif?t=1713699823\" width=577 height=116 /></span><br>\"The Strongest Grandma in the World\"<br><br>\"SEOIRYE\" is a 2D platformer game that tells the story of Seo Irye, who sets off on a journey to the underworld to find her missing grandson.<br>This game features adventure elements, item acquisition, and boss battles.<br>As a kind and gentle grandmother who doesn't harm others, you must adopt a strategy of evading enemy attacks.<br><br>Seo Irye is now seeking three guardians to join forces with them and locate her own grandson.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516280/extras/7461f1093eadbbb884dca9444dd2faf3.avif?t=1713699823\" width=577 height=323 /></span><br><br>Please help her successfully find her grandson and return safely!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516280/extras/c298b25b34ca624151039072ab892d12.avif?t=1713699823\" width=577 height=116 /></span><br>\"The Strongest Grandma in the World\"<br><br>\"SEOIRYE\" is a 2D platformer game that tells the story of Seo Irye, who sets off on a journey to the underworld to find her missing grandson.<br>This game features adventure elements, item acquisition, and boss battles.<br>As a kind and gentle grandmother who doesn't harm others, you must adopt a strategy of evading enemy attacks.<br><br>Seo Irye is now seeking three guardians to join forces with them and locate her own grandson.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2516280/extras/7461f1093eadbbb884dca9444dd2faf3.avif?t=1713699823\" width=577 height=323 /></span><br><br>Please help her successfully find her grandson and return safely!",
